<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />But evil men will perish.</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh's enemies will be like the glory of the pastures;</para>

<para style="q1">they will be consumed and disappear in the smoke.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />The wicked person borrows but does not repay,</para>

<para style="q1">but the righteous person is generous and gives.</para>
